  "original_title": "\u2019\u2019\u0dbb\u0dcf\u0da2\u0db4\u0d9a\u0dca\u0dc2 \u0dc3\u0dd9\u0dc0\u0db1\u0dd0\u0dbd\u0dd2 \u0d86\u0dab\u0dca\u0da9\u0dd4\u0dc0\u2019\u2019 \u0da2\u0db1\u0dad\u0dcf\u0dc0\u0da7 \u0db6\u0dd0\u0da7 \u0daf\u0dd9\u0db1\u0dc0\u0dcf",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "The \"Shadow Government of Rajapaksa\" is beating the people",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The opposition leader Mr. Sajith Premadasa said in Colombo today (2) that the \"Rajapaksha Shadow Government\" is currently using state violence and state brutality to rally the people.",
        "The leader of the opposition also mentioned that the government has worked to create a new face in the people's society that destroys democracy, so it will stand strongly against it.",
        "He said this in a meeting held at the opposition leader's office in Colombo with the lawyers' community in association with the National People's Assembly for Democracy and Social Justice that the civil community that advocates for democracy is being harassed on the way.",
        "The opposition leader said that in such a situation, a serious responsibility has been assigned to the legal community and expressed his gratitude for their support for the right to life of the country's citizens.",
        "The opposition leader questioned whether the government is trying to give the message to the people that they have lost their democratic right to hold an opinion, express their views, and speak.",
        "Mr. Sajith Premadasa further said that the legal community as well as the responsible citizens of this country are against this violence of the government."
      ],
